Frontend -> POST /signup {name, email, password}
       |
       V
Express route -> matches /signup -> calls signup controller
       |
       V
Controller reads req.body -> checks DB -> calls User.create()
       |
       V
User model pre-save hook -> hashes password -> saves in MongoDB
       |
       V
Controller generates JWT -> sends {user, token} back
       |
       V

Frontend stores token -> user authenticated

Tool	Kya hai?
Redux Toolkit (RTK)	Redux logic banane ka tool
React-Redux	Redux ko React se connect karne ka tool
